mrmc.chart

Class XYPair

  • java.lang.Object
    • mrmc.chart.XYPair
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<XYPair>

    public class XYPair
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<XYPair>
    Helper class to contain XY coordinate data within a single object. Coordinates are comparable such that one coordinate is greater than another if it's x value is greater than the other. If the x coordinates are equal, comparison is determined by the y value.
    Version:
    2.0b
    Author:
    Rohan Pathare
